  <summary date="2017-07-25T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Building Blocks of STEM Act

This bill instructs the National Science Foundation, when awarding grants under the Discovery Research PreK-12 program, to consider age distribution in order to more equitably allocate funding for research studies with a focus on early childhood.</summary>
